This is a drop-in, fun for all, do art yourself place where we help you love making art! We offer an incredible variety of projects including: - glass tile mosaics - paint your own pottery - beads and wire - collage and decoupage - wet clay - art for kids Just come in and choose a project. We will help you every step of the way! Adowntown fixture since the '50s. Rightly famous for its omelettes (over 265 of them). Breakfast items are now served all day due to popular demand. The dinner menu is classic American fare.
